# Using the shopping cart

1. set up org.openpsa.products as your see fit
2. create a topic for net.nemein.shoppingcart
3. in your site style add call to display the cart
    <?php
    $_MIDCOM->componentloader->load('net.nemein.shoppingcart');
    net_nemein_shoppingcart_render_shortlist_iframe();
    ?>
   (see net/nemein/shoppingcart/helpers.php if you wish to display it differently)
4. Where displaying producst add call to create "add to cart" links
    <?php net_nemein_shoppingcart_render_additem_shortlist($data['product']); ?>
5. test the cart
6. configure checkout backend
7. profit
